\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"020efbd42f95f7bd2e760751b9cb2f70affc34b0","tid":2506395,"uid":45660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b5623d72333c140f8afc6ec3846a27ee2ece48","tid":2506395,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"原文Link<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9507749/amp/How-scientists-Wuhan-lab-helped-Chinese-army-secret-project-animal-viruses.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-9507749%2Famp%2FHow-scientists-Wuhan-lab-helped-Chinese-army-secret-project-animal-viruses.html&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=8cbf36ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9507749/amp/How-scientists-Wuhan-lab-helped-Chinese-army-secret-project-animal-viruses.html</a><br />\n<br />\nWorrying new clues about the origins of Covid: How scientists at Wuhan lab helped Chinese army in secret project to find animal viruses, writes IAN BIRRELL"},{"pid":"3abd851d80aa5e5495008ba428e31b15d415ec05","tid":2506395,"uid":396921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1af2c57e9e8a4d5a6bf70d44fc4aeb879a8a2af8","tid":2506395,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cd4875bdf3abea4b75e8ffb09a2ab0ca7e8e80c6","tid":2506395,"uid":396921,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"499576e92d9d1ba4c7afcd33aa5078b96916171c","tid":2506395,"uid":33263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:59:40.000Z","msg":"印度佬唔開戰 唔核平中國 真係唔好叫自己印度國"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:02:18.000Z","msg":"分分鐘搞到滅撚埋國都似，人口密度又高，衛生意識又弱，又多窮人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:05:17.000Z","msg":"最重要都係研究到藥物治療<br />\n閻麗夢都話<br />\nhydroxychloroquine可以醫<br />\n但沒人聽<br />\n<br />\n因為呢隻藥幫唔到藥廠賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:11:17.000Z","msg":"印度咖哩科技醫療都唔弱，好多歐美貴藥佢地都有平價翻版，只能靠佢地盡早自救"},{"pid":"2fd254636ccc3f0fcbfbf8093efc5218c75a652b","tid":2506395,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:11:45.000Z","msg":"Scientists at Wuhan lab were on massive project investigating animal viruses <br />\n<br />\nDocuments obtained by The Mail on Sunday have revealed a nationwide scheme<br />\n<br />\nIt was being directed by leading state body, which was launched nine years ago <br />\n<br />\nIts aim was to find new viruses and detect 'dark matter' of biology involved in spreading disease - alongside military officials, despite denials of any such links"}],"pinned":{"pid":"316a87bb11fcc518e2bf66c2125e18cb42f39aa0","tid":2506395,"uid":33263,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國軍方封鎖武漢病毒研究所關鍵數據庫 含約1400種蝙蝠病毒<br />\n<br />\n3月時，追查病毒起源的跨國團隊「DRASTIC」發布25頁調查報告，揭露中國武漢病毒研究所有至少15座數據庫無預警離線，無法讓外部人員進入查看，而數據庫管理員正是石正麗，另備受爭議的主要數據庫「<a href=\"http://batvirus.whiov.ac.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbatvirus.whiov.ac.cn&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=8a232f12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">batvirus.whiov.ac.cn</a>」也被封鎖，此數據庫據信存有2.2萬個病毒樣本及病毒基因序列、1.5萬個蝙蝠樣本，並包含1400種蝙蝠病毒；據稱，「<a href=\"http://batvirus.whiov.ac.cn\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbatvirus.whiov.ac.cn&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oF%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=8a232f12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">batvirus.whiov.ac.cn</a>」自2019年9月就被封鎖，不開放外界查看，直至2019年12月30日才稱完成更新，無獨有偶，中共正是在這一天對外宣稱發現「新型病毒」。<br />\n<br />\n疫情延燒至今，中國仍舊不肯分享重要訊息，而《星期日郵報》掌握文件指出，曹務春與石正麗在「動物源病原體的發現及其對人類致病性研究」上進行合作，致力於發掘可感染人類者，並進行進化研究。<br />\n<br />\n該團隊從多次在國際期刊發表研究進度，2018年更新研究進度指出，該團隊已發現4種新病原體和10種新細菌，並使用宏觀基因體（metagenomics）技術發現了1640多種新病毒，這些研究結果都出於石正麗自中國南部洞穴採集之蝙蝠糞便及血液樣本。透過提取遺傳物質，石正麗也在去年發現了「RaTG13」病毒，「RaTG13」是目前已知與致武漢肺炎病毒株最接近一種。<br />\n<br />\n研究的相關資訊都存放在武漢實驗室，使其堪稱亞洲最大蝙蝠冠狀病毒庫；除此之外，石正麗還承認在礦場收集到8種未確認的SARS病毒，然而這間實驗室卻在2019年9月將樣本及數據無預警下線，正巧就在武漢爆發武漢肺炎的幾週前。<br />\n<br />\n中國領導人習近平曾言，科學將成為中國邁向全球霸主之路的關鍵，其後，中國軍方便擴大對科學家的聘用；對此，曾在中國政府工作過的異見人士韓聯超（Lianchao Han，音譯）表示，曹務春的參與研究起人疑竇，恐怕軍方的冠狀病毒研究專家也參與了生物防禦行動。</blockquote>"}}